title: Photoshop Camera RAW 8.5 (CS6 & CC Support)
description:
Downloaded through Adobe Update Management Tool 7.1

Camera Raw 8.5 is applicable for Photoshop CS6 and Photoshop CC.


New Camera Support in Camera Raw 8.5

Canon PowerShot G1 X Mark II
Fujifilm FinePix S1
Nikon 1 J4
Nikon 1 S2
Nikon 1 V3
Olympus OM-D E-M10
Panasonic DMC-GH4
Pentax 645Z
Samsung NX3000
Sony DSC-RX100 III
Sony A7S (ILCE-7S)
Sony Alpha SLT-A77 II (ILCA-77M2)

More info available at: http://blogs.adobe.com/lightroomjournal/2014/06/camera-raw-8-5-and-dng-converter-8-5-now-available.html
